3) Program to check given pin is valid or not
-----------------------------------------------------------
pin=8547
print('enter your pin')
x=int(input())
if(pin==x):
    print('Continue the transaction')
else:
    print('Incorrect pin number. Please try again')
----------------------------------------------------------------
Output:
enter your pin
8547
Continue the transaction
enter your pin
5468
Incorrect pin number. Please try again
*********************************************************
